  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The goal of the project is to create 10 hectares mangrove greenbelt through planting and regenerating 100000 mangrove together with local people in terms of biodiversity, coastal protection, mangrove-based livelihoods promotion as well as climate change adaptation and mitigation. Once there were plenty of mangroves in the periphery of project site but this mangrove has come under severe pressure due to climatic and anthropogenic reasons.</narrative>
